Author: newthhang
Text: I mean what she said is true, it is all about false hopes we give ourselves. I started and failed a few times with my diet, if I could have done it normally and started last summer.. and not start and then stop I would be fine now, if I didn't have that mentality "okay, I will start next week" or "I will start tomorrow" I probably won't be restricting so hard now and then having this moment of slipping and then purging.   I really hope you get rid of the purging and get better.

Author: NewBullMoose
Text: Proud of you :) keep it up!
